					<div class="story-content-container">
						<h2><a href="https://lithub.com/how-a-democracy-descends-into-murderous-fascism-on-pinochets-chile/" title="How a Democracy Descends Into Murderous Fascism: On Pinochet’s Chile">How a Democracy Descends Into Murderous Fascism: On Pinochet’s Chile</a></h2>
					</div>
				</div>
